{"about_the_game":"<strong>The Oily Depths</strong> is a short horror game set in a submarine deep beneath the sea. You must locate and drill for oil or your corporate overlords will stop your supply of oxygen.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PILOT YOUR SUB</h2>Utilize all your gauges, meters, and monitors as your visibility is limited within the sub. Carefully navigate the sea floor to locate the oil extraction targets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/helm_gif.gif?t=1728473822\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OPERATE DANGEROUS DRILLING MACHINERY</h2>Flip levers, grab tools, set locking-arms, and more. You will need to gain a mastery of each part of your equipment until it's a part of you...<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/drill_gif.gif?t=1728473822\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AVOID DROWNING, BURNING ALIVE, OR BEING EATEN...</h2>&quot;Not our problem. If you don't meet quota... We cut your oxygen.&quot;<br>-Corporate<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/fireflood_gif.gif?t=1728473822\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728473822","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728473822","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/4520a9e8820071f686d6407d05ed8db4a67e3a94/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728473822","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/4520a9e8820071f686d6407d05ed8db4a67e3a94/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728473822","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Depictions of suffocation and drowning"},"detai